<h3>Find the corresponding information for this product as it is listed on the given URL.</h3>

<div class="highlight-box">
<h4>Instructions:</h4>
<ol>
	<li>Got to the Product Listing URL below.</li>
	<li>Find where the product is listed on the page.</li>
	<li>Enter the details in the form below.</li>
</ol>
<h4>Notes:</h4>
<ul>
	<li>Every product will have a name and a price.</li>
	<li>Not every product will have a description.</li>
	<li>Not every product will have an image.</li>
	<li>The image URL must be a <strong>direct link to the image file</strong>.</li>
</ul>
</div>

<center>
<p><a href="http://i.imgur.com/3KSaUla.png" target="_blank">Examples of Product Listings</a></p>
</center>

<table>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">Product Listing URL:</td>
			<td class="field"><a href="${url}" target="_blank">${url}</a></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">Product Number:</td>
			<td class="field">${product_number}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">Product Name:</td>
			<td class="field"><input id="product_name" name="product_name" type="text" /><span class="required"> REQUIRED - DO NOT INCLUDE PRODUCT NUMBER!</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">Product Image URL:</td>
			<td class="field"><input id="product_image" name="product_image" type="text" /><span class="notice">**MUST LINK DIRECTLY TO IMAGE FILE.**</span></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="label">Product Description:</td>
			<td class="field"><textarea id="product_description" name="product_description"></textarea></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2"><br />
			<strong>This product is missing something:</strong></td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="field" colspan="2"><input id="no_image" name="no_image" type="checkbox" /> Product does not have an image.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="field" colspan="2"><input id="no_description" name="no_description" type="checkbox" /> Product does not have a description.</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td class="field" colspan="2"><input id="no_product" name="no_product" type="checkbox" /> Can&#39;t find the product.</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>
